{"tid":1685341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11月2日遮打同愛丁堡有不反，最啱由維園行過去","createTime":"2019-10-31T13:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T13:30:40.000Z","uid":143608,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c45e67f5f703245f2540fbd95a4ea94ef1452e8c","tid":1685341,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"維園的集會警方發出反對通知書，愛國愛港又守法的連登仔又點會參加呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係愛丁堡同遮打有不反，我地要去合法表達訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期六天氣咁舒服，最啱港島半日遊，由維園出發去愛丁橋同遮打。警告你班連登仔，唔好抄我路線，搞到條馬路都企滿人就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4b3a9ddc7639fcd991088634dbb1c34e2c8ce7","tid":1685341,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"星期六遠足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d241342712cdb62c7abaf77546d2aa0c5ce032","tid":1685341,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b45d2d33cc0cff3b0020ed3063d65a29478ea910","tid":1685341,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"星期六，港島見"},{"pid":"319c47f232ad63f1e49f408f33a47312cb6d78b7","tid":1685341,"uid":143608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"推！"}]}